    "en": {
      "title": "The number of injured in the protests has risen to 84",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior spokesman said that 84 people injured in the protests near the Colombo and Battaramulla Polduwa junction have been admitted to the Colombo National Hospital.",
        "Among them are an army officer, two police officers, two journalists and five women, the spokesman said.",
        "The spokesman added that forty-two people were injured in yesterday's protests and forty-two people were injured during the protest near Polduwa intersection in Battaramulla."
      ],
